{"tid":248582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國集資起樓陷阱 19港人中招","createTime":"2017-05-18T16:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T06:39:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1daac410bc599b2c587a1f564205a2289cb649d","tid":248582,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170518/large/1495116681_f43e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170518%2Flarge%2F1495116681_f43e.jpg&h=f17ba167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7名內地人到西環中聯辦請願，聲稱在惠東買樓受騙。(劉漢權攝)<br />\n<br />\n 港人墮內地買樓陷阱。港人邱女士今年3月與家人到惠東碧桂園十里銀灘玩耍時，有中介公司推介她們購買附近稔山鎮鹽灶背石碑坑村興建的一幢17層高樓房，指每平方米售價2千至3千元，對方聲稱因無房產證才平售，並稱是集資建樓，得到村委的支持，不會有問題。<br />\n<br />\n她與家人見樓價便宜，心想買來自住沒房產證也沒問題，遂購買兩個單位，當時樓層已建至5樓，簽約時合共交了19萬元人民幣，至4月樓房建至8樓時，又再交11.4萬元人民幣，但在建至12樓時，獲通知國土局以樓房違法興建及非法買賣，需要清拆。<br />\n<br />\n邱指，本周日到惠東與發展商商討賠償問題，對方提出3個解決方案，其中最好的一個方案，是發展商退回7成支付的樓款，先付3成，其餘款項，要在業主簽署協議書及交回合約後，於3個月內分兩次清還，業主擔心簽協議書及交還合約後，其餘欠款對方會拖延不還，變成錢債糾紛，故拒絕簽署。事件中有另外18名香港苦主。<br />\n<br />\n今晨10時許，7名內地苦主到西環中聯辦請願，其中文女士聲稱，在地產經紀游說下，以11萬元人民幣購買惠東碧桂園十里銀灘附近稔山鎮鹽灶背石碑坑村一幢新廈的樓花，興建期間被當地政府指未有房產證，需要清拆。她稱，代理商聲稱本周歸還3成樓款給她們，其餘7成稍後交還，文懷疑受騙，對方有意拖延她們樓款，遂來港到中聯辦投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170518/large/1495116683_d5dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170518%2Flarge%2F1495116683_d5dd.jpg&h=fc10eaf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n苦主文女士懷疑墮買樓陷阱，與6名內地苦主到西環中聯辦請願。(劉漢權攝)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170518/56712520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170518%2F56712520&d=uTsTvEvhFTFW0ksY74cvWk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=71d61be8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170518%2F56712520&h=ddbc758e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170518/56712520</a>"},{"pid":"73c73314e4684ac0858b9dbd1a61c6b0cbb5f464","tid":248582,"uid":25787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:15:28.000Z","msg":"好人好姐去支那買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b71b711067ae54069b95a625ab29d1dd19c7cac","tid":248582,"uid":100010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"大陸人黎香港請願？"},{"pid":"99b4ec08f164fb4e8c8d9c10c90085effe68f898","tid":248582,"uid":60020,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:22:13.000Z","msg":"黎香港做乜，自己去北京上訴喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a8c012e41635d7f655d873067511bac5128c89","tid":248582,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人黎香港請願？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270ca2f6f2f9b476f3ce1e7a8a9af9d67ebc418d","tid":248582,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T16:28:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貪貧貪貧貪貧貪貧......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"08ae47c637039cfaad4b73ec643d754f0e42e315","tid":248582,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"返大陸買樓花咁大膽?<br />\n<br />\n就算起好晒, 只要當地機關一句重新發展, 就可以剷平佢再起第二樣..."},{"pid":"ae67750d6efc32f543cc784bd5b31259fe9ba960","tid":248582,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20